	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're a teenager, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You carry more than people see — the anxiety that won't switch off, the comparison that follows you everywhere, the quiet question of whether you're actually enough. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on your phone — and it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> from beginning to end. Whether you searched "Bible verses for teenagers," "verses for teens," "youth Bible verses for anxiety," or just need some encouragement — the answer starts in one place: your worth was never your grades, your looks, or your follower count. You are His beloved, right now, before you achieve a single thing.`}
