		{ ref: `1 Timothy 4:12`, slug: `1-timothy`, ch: 4, text: `Don't let anyone look down on you because you are young, but set an example in speech, in conduct, in love, in faith, and in purity.`, note: `Being young isn't a disqualification — your Father can use your life to show others what He's like, starting now.` },
		{ ref: `Isaiah 43:1`, slug: `isaiah`, ch: 43, text: `Fear not, for I have redeemed you; I have called you by name — you are Mine, says your Father.`, note: `You're not a number or a username to Him. He knows your name, and He calls you His own.` },
